    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. To make him sound even more like a man of his time, can you make it more detailed? Have him talk about how they lack proper religion or science, and how they seem almost stuck in a state of nature. Maybe mention how their very existence justifies why a more 'advanced' nation needs to step in and manage things for them.",
